branchCategory.name: CY3
branchCategory.description: <p>Rodless Cylinder, magnetically coupled series 90-CY3 and 91-CY3 can be used in many diverse&nbsp; environments.&nbsp;90-CY3 is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 91-CY3 includes a "Lub-retainer" and is compatible with low dew point (40&deg;C) applications.&nbsp;Magnetically coupled cylinders have a wide range of&nbsp; applications, and save mounting space. Loads and moments are possible&nbsp; through the use of integrated guides.&nbsp;</p>

branchItem.name: 90/91-CY3B, Magnetically Coupled Rodless Cylinder, (Basic)
branchItem.description: <p>Rodless Cylinder, magnetically coupled series 90-CY3B and 91-CY3B can be used in many diverse  environments. 90-CY3B is made from materials compatible with secondary battery manufacturing. 91-CY3B includes a "Lub-retainer" and is compatible with low dew point (40°C) applications. Magnetically coupled cylinders have a wide range of  applications, and save mounting space. Loads and moments are possible  through the use of integrated guides. A variety of guides can be used  to achieve the necessary accuracy or allowable moment needed for your  application. CY is available in 5 bore sizes, from 15mm to 40mm with  standard stokes up to 1000mm. </p>
